---
import Container from "@/components/container.astro";
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Link from "@/components/ui/link.astro";
---

<Layout title="About — Jason Fallas Contracting | Building Dreams in NJ">
  <Container>
    <div class="mt-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight text-center">
        About Jason Fallas Contracting
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl mt-6 text-slate-600 text-center">
        Expert craftsmanship and reliable service across Union, Morris, and Warren County, New Jersey.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-16 prose prose-lg">
      <h2>Our Approach</h2>
      <p>
        At JF Contracting, we bring your vision to life with precision, craftsmanship, and care. We specialize in delivering high-quality construction, renovations, and home improvement services across New Jersey.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        From complete home renovations to custom carpentry and detailed 3D renderings, we approach every project with the same commitment to quality. Whether it's refinishing hardwood floors, remodeling a commercial space like Perch H&C in Maplewood, or building custom cabinetry, we deliver results that exceed expectations.
      </p>

      <h2>What Sets Us Apart</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Expert Craftsmanship:</strong> Years of experience in carpentry, painting, renovations, and general contracting.</li>
        <li><strong>Custom Solutions:</strong> Every project is tailored to your specific needs and vision.</li>
        <li><strong>Trusted Network:</strong> We work with reliable subcontractors for plumbing, electrical, and specialized trades.</li>
        <li><strong>3D Visualization:</strong> See your project before we build with professional 3D renderings.</li>
        <li><strong>Professional Service:</strong> Clear communication, reliable timelines, and quality workmanship on every job.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Our Work</h2>
      <p>
        We've completed projects ranging from residential renovations to commercial build-outs, including notable work for <strong>Perch H&C in Maplewood</strong>—a stunning retail and café space featuring a curated goods shop, gelato window, coffee and mocktail bar, and event rental facilities.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our portfolio includes kitchen and bathroom remodels, hardwood floor refinishing, custom carpentry, painting, garage installations, and comprehensive general contracting services.
      </p>

      <h2>Service Area</h2>
      <p>We focus on two main clusters for efficient scheduling and fast response:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Summit / Short Hills / Mendham corridor</strong> — including Chatham, Springfield, and Union</li>
        <li><strong>Blairstown & Warren County</strong> — our new local base for steady residential work</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Nearby? <a href="/contact">Contact us</a> to confirm coverage—we often take high‑value projects just outside these areas.</p>
    </div>

  <div class="bg-brand text-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-lg mt-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
        Let's Work Together
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mb-6">
        Ready to start your project? Call for a free estimate or request a quote online.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <Link href="tel:+1-609-598-6392" style="inverted">
          Call (609) 598-6392
        </Link>
        <Link href="/contact" style="outline">
          Request a Quote
        </Link>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>
</Layout>

---
